#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.tan.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.tan"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:1 of
msgid "Compute tangent element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算正切值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:3 of
msgid "Equivalent to ``mt.sin(x)/mt.cos(x)`` element-wise."
msgstr "等价于逐元素计算 ``mt.sin(x)/mt.cos(x)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:5 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的原始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:17 of
msgid "**y** -- The corresponding tangent values."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的正切值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:22 of
msgid ""
"If `out` is provided, the function writes the result into it, and returns"
" a reference to `out`.  (See Examples)"
msgstr "如果提供了 `out`，函数会将结果写入其中并返回对 `out` 的引用。（参见示例）"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:26 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:27 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I. A. Stegun, Handbook of Mathematical Functions. New "
"York, NY: Dover, 1972."
msgstr "M. Abramowitz 和 I. A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，纽约：Dover，1972 年。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tan.tan:31 of
msgid "示例"
